snippet.title: DeltaFall Trailer - Underevent 2024
snippet.description:
This is the official re-upload of the DeltaFall trailer from this year's UnderEvent! Watch as the Light-Gang traverse Ideation's deep laboratory labyrinth, and evade Neon in this DeltaRune fan game made in Godot engine! Game made by @hipxel, and the Team!

Three thumbnail changes in one day? Nuh uh, no way.

Discord:
https://discord.gg/qx3z5Gw6ky
Gamejolt:
https://gamejolt.com/games/deltafall/863784
Songs:
https://soundcloud.com/deltafall/besmirched-df-trailer-full
Supporting Curly's songs directly;
https://youtu.be/0wfoAgwzi6o
https://youtu.be/m9oAf3TKGfA
